Description: Allow to visualise data on the NCBI phylogenetic tree as presented in Lifemap '<http://lifemap.univ-lyon1.fr/>'. It takes an input a dataframe with at least a "taxid" column containing NCBI format TaxIds and allow to draw multiple layers with different visualisation tools.
